emscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">lot</a>=C2=A0around here=C2=A0over =
the last couple of years is that, as all the=C2=A0stocks are increasingly o=
wned by the same handful of giant diversified index=C2=A0and quasi-index in=
vestors, those giant investors will think of themselves less as owners of p=
articular companies and more as owners of=C2=A0<em>the economy</em>. To the=
 extent that they think at all about their portfolio companies=E2=80=99 bus=
iness decisions, they will not ask questions like =E2=80=9Cdoes this decisi=
on maximize this company=E2=80=99s profits=E2=80=9D but rather =E2=80=9Cis =
this decision good for the world,=E2=80=9D because they=C2=A0<em>own the wo=
rld</em>.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Of course they don=E2=80=99t own=
=C2=A0<em>the world</em>; they own a large sample of the=C2=A0<em>equity </=
em>in the=C2=A0world=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>public companies</em>. The thesis h=
ere is not, like, =E2=80=9CBlackRock Inc. are our benevolent overlords and =
will make decisions for the good of society.=E2=80=9D If there=E2=80=99s so=
me decision that is in the long-term interests of corporate shareholders, a=
s a class, but bad for corporate employees, as a class, then presumably Bla=
ckRock will prefer that shareholders win. But they really are diversified a=
nd long-term holders, and in the long run the interests of shareholders are=
=C2=A0<em>pretty=C2=A0</em>good. Like you want=C2=A0a booming global econom=
y, rising productivity,=C2=A0increasing wealth and consumption, stable gove=
rnments, the rule of law, minimal extreme weather events and pandemics, etc=
.; the overlap between =E2=80=9Cgood stuff for the world=E2=80=9D and =E2=
=80=9Cgood stuff for public-company shareholders=E2=80=9D is not=C2=A0<em>p=
erfect=C2=A0</em>but it is=C2=A0<em>large</em>.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">We have talked a lot about two particular applications of this. One is=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25093534.264700/a=
