7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Covid-=
19 vaccines</a>: If you are BlackRock, and one of your portfolio companies =
develops a Covid-19 vaccine and is like =E2=80=9Cwe would like to roll this=
