=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I think that this stuff is interesting but=C2=A0you ca=
n definitely be a skeptic. Roberto Tallarita of Harvard Law School is a ske=
ptic; here is his recent paper on =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
